PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of CHARLES MALONE of Camox, British Columbia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Development Investment Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Carole Malo, whose term has expired.
